title: Steph Curry Scores 62, New-Look Rockets, Heat-Celtics | WHAT’S BURNIN’ | Ep. 2
itunes:title: Steph Curry Scores 62, New-Look Rockets, Heat-Celtics | WHAT’S BURNIN’ | Ep. 2
description:
On this weeks WHAT’S BURNIN’, Matt and Stak breakdown a crazy week in the NBA which was capped off by Steph Curry dropping 62 on the Blazers. The boys talk the new-look Rockets, the Eastern Conferences unexpected early-season standings. Plus, they discuss the Suns & Sixers hot starts.
